00:59:20,500 --> 00:59:21,800
Because he's Mr. Ma's subordinate.

561
00:59:22,800 --> 00:59:25,800
You're afraid that if Jiu was caught, he would expose you.

562
00:59:26,100 --> 00:59:26,800
That's not true!

563
00:59:54,800 --> 00:59:57,800
Our people have been searching for Jiu everywhere, but didn't find him.

564
01:00:01,800 --> 01:00:02,800
We have a lot of people.

565
01:00:04,800 --> 01:00:07,800
But we can't even find him.

566
01:00:08,800 --> 01:00:09,800
That upsets me.

567
01:00:12,800 --> 01:00:14,800
And who do you believe?

568
01:00:15,800 --> 01:00:16,800
Madam Li or Madam Chan.

569
01:00:18,800 --> 01:00:19,800
I don't believe both.

570
01:00:21,800 --> 01:00:22,800
What should I do?

571
01:00:23,800 --> 01:00:27,800
How can I know what happened exactly?

572
01:00:28,800 --> 01:00:30,800
What is Tian's secret?

573
01:00:32,800 --> 01:00:34,800
I will hurry to find Jiu.

574
01:00:35,800 --> 01:00:38,800
If we catch him, things will become clearer.

575
01:01:00,800 --> 01:01:01,800
Yang.

576
01:01:05,800 --> 01:01:06,800
How is Jiu?

577
01:01:09,800 --> 01:01:10,800
He could run away.

578
01:01:18,800 --> 01:01:19,800
I'm sorry, Yang.

579
01:01:21,800 --> 01:01:24,800
I got you into trouble again.

580
01:01:27,800 --> 01:01:28,800
I'm fine.

581
01:01:29,800 --> 01:01:31,800
Really. Get some rest.

582
01:01:32,400 --> 01:01:32,900
Yang.

583
01:01:36,800 --> 01:01:37,800
Actually...

584
01:01:39,800 --> 01:01:40,800
Jiu and I...

585
01:01:43,800 --> 01:01:45,800
We are...

586
01:01:46,300 --> 01:01:46,800
I know that/

587
01:01:48,800 --> 01:01:49,800
Don't say anything.

588
01:01:52,800 --> 01:01:53,800
Do you know about it?

589
01:02:15,800 --> 01:02:16,800
Do you think...

590
01:02:18,800 --> 01:02:20,800
Do you think I'm stupid?

591
01:02:25,800 --> 01:02:26,800
I'm like a fool

592
01:02:30,800 --> 01:02:32,800
for thinking that someone would love me

593
01:02:33,800 --> 01:02:34,800
even though...

594
01:02:41,800 --> 01:02:43,800
I don't deserve real love.

595
01:02:45,800 --> 01:02:46,800
Tian.

596
01:02:47,800 --> 01:02:48,800
Listen to me.

597
01:02:50,800 --> 01:02:51,800
Don't think like that.

598
01:02:52,800 --> 01:02:53,800
Don't blame yourself.

599
01:02:56,800 --> 01:02:58,800
Everything that happened wasn't your fault.

600
01:03:02,800 --> 01:03:05,800
You're just unlucky that you fell in love with the wrong guy.

601
01:03:06,800 --> 01:03:09,800
Loving someone who deceived you for benefits.

602
01:03:10,800 --> 01:03:12,800
He's bad.

603
01:03:14,800 --> 01:03:16,800
It's not that you're not worthy of a good love.

604
01:03:22,800 --> 01:03:23,800
Tian.

605
01:03:24,800 --> 01:03:25,800
For me,

606
01:03:27,800 --> 01:03:28,800
you are a very good brother.

607
01:03:30,800 --> 01:03:31,800
You're considerate.

608
01:03:33,800 --> 01:03:35,800
And most importantly, you are the person I love

609
01:03:36,800 --> 01:03:39,800
and I want my loved one to be the happiest.

610
01:03:41,800 --> 01:03:43,800
If you think that no one loves you,

611
01:03:44,800 --> 01:03:45,800
I want you to know that

612
01:03:48,800 --> 01:03:49,800
I love you.

613
01:03:50,800 --> 01:03:52,800
And I will always be beside you, brother.

614
01:04:22,800 --> 01:04:23,800
Madam.

615
01:04:24,800 --> 01:04:26,800
Chan saw us using the orchid.

616
01:04:27,200 --> 01:04:28,800
Yang also know about Mr. Tian's secret.

617
01:04:29,800 --> 01:04:32,800
If we leave them, they must be a threat to us in the future.

618
01:04:33,800 --> 01:04:34,800
What should we do?

619
01:04:35,800 --> 01:04:36,800
Mr. Song is watching us now.

620
01:04:37,800 --> 01:04:40,800
If Yang or Chan is dead or disappears,

621
01:04:41,800 --> 01:04:43,800
Mr. Song definitely won't let this matter quiet.

622
01:04:44,500 --> 01:04:45,800
But anyway, we have to find a way to kill them.

623
01:05:10,800 --> 01:05:11,800
Tonight,

624
01:05:12,800 --> 01:05:14,800
you lure Yang to the back of the house.

625
01:05:15,800 --> 01:05:16,800
Then use the orchid to kill him.

626
01:05:20,800 --> 01:05:21,800
How about Madam Chan?

627
01:05:22,800 --> 01:05:24,800
When Yang disappears,

628
01:05:25,800 --> 01:05:26,800
she will probably look for him.

629
01:05:28,800 --> 01:05:30,800
We will kill her by then.

630
01:05:32,800 --> 01:05:33,800
And when the other two are gone,

631
01:05:34,800 --> 01:05:37,800
we will claim that they run away because of guilt

632
01:05:38,800 --> 01:05:39,800
siding with Mr. Ma.

633
01:05:46,800 --> 01:05:47,800
Aunt Jia.

634
01:05:48,800 --> 01:05:50,800
Didn't you say that Tian want to talk to me?

635
01:05:51,800 --> 01:05:52,800
And where is him?

636
01:05:54,800 --> 01:05:57,800
Wait a minute, Mr. Tian is coming.

637
01:06:27,800 --> 01:06:28,800
The wind direction is just right.

638
01:06:34,800 --> 01:06:36,800
Aunt Jia, what is this?

639
01:06:37,800 --> 01:06:39,800
I think I'd better meet him at his room.

640
01:06:50,800 --> 01:06:51,800
Mr. Yang.

641
01:07:05,800 --> 01:07:06,800
Mr. Tian.

642
01:07:07,100 --> 01:07:07,800
Tian.

643
01:07:11,800 --> 01:07:12,800
Tian.

644
01:07:13,800 --> 01:07:14,800
What are you doing?

645
01:07:15,100 --> 01:07:15,800
Come here.

646
01:07:16,000 --> 01:07:16,800
Tian.

647
01:07:17,000 --> 01:07:17,800
Go wash your hands. / Tian.

648
01:07:18,100 --> 01:07:18,800
Tian.

649
01:07:19,100 --> 01:07:19,800
Get out.

650
01:07:20,100 --> 01:07:20,800
No.

651
01:07:21,100 --> 01:07:21,800
Wash your hands.

652
01:07:22,100 --> 01:07:23,800
Hurry up, Madam. / Right now.

653
01:07:24,100 --> 01:07:24,800
What are you doing? Huh?

654
01:08:01,800 --> 01:08:04,800
How is it? Is it in time?

655
01:08:05,800 --> 01:08:06,800
Yes.

656
01:08:07,100 --> 01:08:08,800
Fortunately, Mr. Tian did not inhale the dust.

657
01:08:10,800 --> 01:08:11,800
What did you do?

658
01:08:13,800 --> 01:08:14,800
You ordered Aunt Jia to kill Yang?

659
01:08:15,800 --> 01:08:16,800
This is too much, Mother.

660
01:08:17,800 --> 01:08:20,800
I need to do it. Yang knew all.

661
01:08:21,100 --> 01:08:21,800
If anything happens to Yang.

662
01:08:22,800 --> 01:08:24,800
you prepare a funeral for me.

663
01:08:25,300 --> 01:08:25,800
Tian.

664
01:08:26,800 --> 01:08:27,800
Don't say that.

665
01:08:28,400 --> 01:08:28,900
Madam didn't want to do it.

666
01:08:29,800 --> 01:08:30,800
She herself was very sad.

667
01:08:32,800 --> 01:08:35,800
You knew why she had to do it.

668
01:08:36,000 --> 01:08:36,800
I know.

669
01:08:37,800 --> 01:08:39,800
But couldn't you do that?

670
01:08:40,800 --> 01:08:43,800
Can you stop this? I beg you.

671
01:08:48,800 --> 01:08:49,800
Yes.

672
01:08:50,800 --> 01:08:51,800
So,

673
01:08:52,800 --> 01:08:56,800
on the association meeting day, you have to announce your marriage.

674
01:08:57,400 --> 01:08:57,900
I will find you a woman.

675
01:08:58,800 --> 01:09:00,800
Get married and take the position of the leader.

676
01:09:06,800 --> 01:09:08,800
It's too late, Mother.

677
01:09:11,800 --> 01:09:12,800
Jiu told Mr. Ma already.

678
01:09:16,800 --> 01:09:18,800
That I am a homosexual.

679
01:09:21,800 --> 01:09:22,800
What?

680
01:10:16,800 --> 01:10:19,800
You still insist that I should announce the marriage?

681
01:10:20,100 --> 01:10:23,800
If you do everything as I said, everyone will be safe.

682
01:10:24,800 --> 01:10:25,800
Look at this first.

683
01:10:27,800 --> 01:10:28,800
Sir.

684
01:10:29,000 --> 01:10:29,800
Sir.

685
01:10:30,100 --> 01:10:31,800
Tian's secret.

686
01:10:33,800 --> 01:10:34,800
Catch him.
